Package: exrcise
Type: Package
Title: Selectively Excise Code Chunks for Exercises
Version: 0.1.0
Authors@R: person(c("Joshua", "A."), "Shapiro", 
                  email = "josh.shapiro@ccdatalab.org",
                  comment = list(ORCID = "0000-0002-6224-0347"),
                  role = c("aut", "cre"))
Maintainer: Joshua Shapiro <josh.shapiro@ccdatalab.org>
Description: This package selectively removes the contents of code chunks from 
    Rmarkdown files to produce new notebooks suitable for live coding instruction
    or exercises, while preserving the original file as a reference or answer key.
